{"tid":159796,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國薩德之眼即將抵韓 中國的夢魘！","createTime":"2017-03-17T09:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T10:08:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7bf8110c6a09eaaeb27dd83f1a32f6cffab8948","tid":159796,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:07:01.000Z","msg":"2017-03-16 <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpGEUi0R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpGEUi0R.jpg&h=ca03b7eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n薩德組裝部件陸續抵達韓國。（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕韓中因部署薩德反導系統關係緊張，韓媒報導，號稱「薩德之眼」的薩德反導系統火控雷達即將抵韓。港媒指出，「薩德之眼」探測距離達1000到2000公里，範圍深入中國境內東北、華北及東南沿海部分地區，削弱中國戰略威懾力。<br />\n《韓聯社》報導，韓國政府人士透露，薩德反導系統AN/TPY-2火控雷達和發射架即將於1到2天內抵達韓國烏山空軍基地，之後會被運往慶尚北道，雷達下個月就會進行運作測試。報導指出，一整套薩德系統包括車載式發射架、AN/TPT-2雷達、防空導彈、移動戰術指揮中心、發電機和冷卻器。<br />\n報導指出，該政府人士表示，薩德裝備具體日程無法一一公開，但韓美將盡早完成薩德的部署。<br />\n《香港01》報導，薩德雷達系統探測距離達1000至2000公里，深入中國境內東北、華北及東南沿海部分地區，用於監控中國戰略導彈動向，因此中國政府對韓國部署薩德表示強烈不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2006188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2006188&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=d5a8d616\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2006188&h=6c330ba7\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2006188</a>"},{"pid":"83adb38566fe910ab1f0632e83b2a52250854707","tid":159796,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6228de85ecce67d22b881ab051f7653ec01c607","tid":159796,"uid":2333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdbe7404f666b8b346dbf68